@startuml
actor "答辩录入员" as DefenseSecretary
actor "教学秘书/专业负责人" as Publisher
participant "答辩页面" as DefensePage
participant "ScoreController" as Controller
participant "DefenseRecord" as DefenseRecord
participant "ScoreSheet" as ScoreSheet

DefenseSecretary -> DefensePage : 录入答辩成绩
DefensePage -> Controller : saveDefenseScore(studentId, score)
Controller -> DefenseRecord : 保存答辩成绩

Publisher -> Controller : publishScore(studentId)
Controller -> ScoreSheet : 汇总指导、评阅、答辩成绩
Controller -> ScoreSheet : 计算 finalScore
Controller -> ScoreSheet : 更新为已发布
Controller --> Publisher : 返回发布结果
@enduml
